1. *Veštica* je bila strašna, ali je bila i dobra. (The witch was scary, but she was also good.)

2. U srednjovekovnom vremenu, *veštice* su bile proglašavane za krivce za sve bolesti. (In the Middle Ages, witches were blamed for all illnesses.)

3. *Veštica* je bila u stanju da pomogne seljacima koji su živeli u okolini. (The witch was able to help the peasants living in the vicinity.)

4. Rečeno je da *veštice* poseduju moć da preoblikuju sebe u životinje. (It is said that witches possess the power to transform themselves into animals.)

5. *Veštičin* čarobni štap je bio napravljen od drveta iz svete šume. (The witch's magic wand was made of wood from a sacred forest.)